# Backend Rules

## Port

API runs on **8001**. Changing it breaks frontend proxy and mobile client.

## HTTP Clients

Use the shared `httpx.AsyncClient` in `routes/places.py` (`_get_http()`). Never create `async with httpx.AsyncClient() as client:` per-request -- it wastes a TCP+TLS handshake every call.

## Family Routes

`routes/family.py` is a Coming Soon stub (returns 503). Do not restore the full family CRUD unless explicitly asked.

## Environment

- `config.py` loads `.env` and exports all secrets
- `database.py` has a singleton Supabase client via `get_supabase()`
- `limiter.py` handles rate limiting with Redis fallback to in-memory
- Production requires `CORS_ORIGINS`, strong `JWT_SECRET` (32+ chars), and all Stripe/Supabase keys
